<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.3.7">
<l>paravi neñcē toḻutu meḻupō yavaṉpālamāy</l>
<l>iravum nāḷu miṉikkaṇ tuyilā tirunteṉpayaṉ</l>
<l>viravi muttam neṭuveṇ maṇalmēl koṇṭuveṇtirai</l>
<l>puravi yeṉṉap putañcey tuvantun tupullāṇiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is the use now of staying night and day, eyes unrested?</l>
<l>Arise, [my] heart; we will worship, being nearby the one who left,</l>
<l rend="indent">praising [him]</l>
<l>In Pullāṇi where white waves, advancing performing leaps like ponies,</l>
<l>Mingling with pearls, carry and cast up [them]</l>
<l rend="indent">onto the long, white sand.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
